where `comul_apply` expands `comul R C c` to `c вКЧ c` (using the fact that `IsCocomm R C` implies `comul R C = id R вКЧ id R`), and `antipode_mul` expands `antipode R C (c вКЧ c)` to `antipode R C c вКЧ antipode R C c`.

